Dear Builder,

AI is reshaping how we live.

It’s exciting, and it’s also a little scary.

The truth is:


No one knows exactly what the future looks like.


But we do know we’re living through one of the most important transitions in human history - one that will define the world our generation leaves behind.

The most valuable thing we can do is help each other move through it.

Build Club started because people needed belonging in a moment of massive change.

We’re here to help you make sense of this new era, one step at a time.

Welcome to Build Club. Let’s build the future we want to live in.

Annie Liao

Founder
